  "text": "Information gain [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] seems particularly adequate since the agent only considers the progress in the learning of dynamics, and the speed of progress is related to the degree of stochasticity. However it is difficult to apply in practice as evidenced by its score. Similarly, related exploration methods (c.f §5.2) in the goal space uses a similar motivation, denoted as learning progress. We saw that it was particularly efficient but hard to compute.",
